#. <section class="sutta" id="sn56.4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.4:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Samādhivagga"
msgstr "1. Immersion"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Dutiyakulaputtasutta"
msgstr "4. Respectable (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.416"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.4:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, atītamaddhānaṃ kulaputtā sammā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ "
"pabbajitā yathābhūtaṃ abhisamesuṃ, sabbe te cattāri ariyasaccāni yathābhūtaṃ "
"abhisamesuṃ."
msgstr "“Mendicants, whatever respectable people—past,"

msgctxt "sn56.4:1.2"
msgid ""
"Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, anāgatamaddhānaṃ kulaputtā sammā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ "
"pabbajitā yathābhūtaṃ abhisamessanti, sabbe te cattāri ariyasaccāni "
"yathābhūtaṃ abhisamessanti."
msgstr "future,"

msgctxt "sn56.4:1.3"
msgid ""
"Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, etarahi kulaputtā sammā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajitā "
"yathābhūtaṃ abhisamenti, sabbe te cattāri ariyasaccāni yathābhūtaṃ "
"abhisamenti."
msgstr ""
"or present—truly comprehend after rightly going forth from the lay life to "
"homelessness, all of them truly comprehend the four noble truths."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.4:2.1"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn56.4:2.2"
msgid ""
"Dukkhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhasamudayaṃ ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhanirodhaṃ "
"ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā ariyasaccaṃ."
msgstr ""
"The noble truths of suffering, the origin of suffering, the cessation of "
"suffering, and the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering. …"

msgctxt "sn56.4:2.3"
msgid ""
"Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, atītamaddhānaṃ kulaputtā sammā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ "
"pabbajitā yathābhūtaṃ abhisamesuṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn56.4:2.4"
msgid "abhisamessanti … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn56.4:2.5"
msgid ""
"abhisamenti, sabbe te imāni cattāri ariyasaccāni yathābhūtaṃ abhisamenti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.4:3.1"
msgid ""
"Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ "
"dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti."
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.4:3.2"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
